description:
Play puzzles from Picross e3 on the Nintendo 3DS™ in Picross S+.

・Picross 150 puzzles
・Mega Picross 150 puzzles

New bonus puzzles will be added to your Gift Box .
・Picross 6 puzzles
・Mega Picross 6 puzzles
・Color Picross 2 puzzles

*Clip Picross puzzles will not be included.
*This content requires the full game, which is sold separately.
name: DLC "Picross e3"
